  <brief_title>Everolimus Versus Placebo in Head and Neck Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Phase II Trial of Everolimus Versus Placebo as Adjuvant Therapy in Patients With Locally Advanced Squamous Cell Cancer of the Head and Neck (SCCHN)</official_title>
